{"tid":2348081,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"辣爆！台E奶女神上下齊開 「黑影走光」畫面瘋傳","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T07:30:55.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"977e1fa2fe048c9849bf7a55b740a57263b09880","tid":2348081,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"「呆萌女神」元元與沈玉琳錄製《11點熱吵店》的網路節目《威廉沈歡樂送》，兩人一起去滑雪，穿著細肩帶平口上衣的元元挑滑雪鞋時頻頻彎腰，直接露奶，讓網友鼻血直流。<br />\n<br />\n元元有著火辣E奶，加上單純個性，頗受網友喜愛。她也很有誠意的穿細肩帶上衣和迷你裙上節目，挑滑雪鞋前，坐在椅子上的元元似乎沒注意到短裙走光問題，被眼尖網友發現，之後才換成褲子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TR1Q02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TR1Q02.jpg&h=b1f08460&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EifVsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EifVsH.jpg&h=cda0876a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2a7b452ff2e40dbfc373e5bae3168e656c8004e","tid":2348081,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"我入到黎"},{"pid":"7c74b6a786e0e1502462cf9509cedb328f5faa90","tid":2348081,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"冇睇台綜廿年，沈玉琳仲係度抽緊o靚妹水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7a32668e029b4bf85de83264f395295fefad9d","tid":2348081,"uid":378879,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vvir19v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvir19v.gif&h=859dacd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4ab466ce14679706c9a0eed82530f8042bb595c","tid":2348081,"uid":82450,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"臨過年都要打搞伯母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858b227afd33c85737f4f1415beaf67f42a7a2cc","tid":2348081,"ui